    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-016__align-001">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-016</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 16.1 - 老子 16.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 16.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>致虛極，守靜篤。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The (state of) vacancy should be brought to the utmost degree, and that of stillness guarded with unwearying vigour.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-016__align-002">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-016</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">3</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 16.3 - 老子 16.5</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 16.2 - 老子 16.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>萬物並作，吾以觀復。夫物芸芸，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>All things alike go through their processes of activity, and (then) we see them return (to their original state). When things (in the vegetable world) have displayed their luxuriant growth, we see each of them return to its root.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-016__align-003">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-016</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 16.6</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 16.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>各復歸其根。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>This returning to their root is what we call the state of stillness;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-016__align-004">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-016</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 16.7</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 16.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>歸根曰靜，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>and that stillness may be called a reporting that they have fulfilled their appointed end.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-016__align-005">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-016</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 16.8</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 16.6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>是謂復命。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The report of that fulfilment is the regular, unchanging rule.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-016__align-006">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-016</prop>
